Get KenPom Game Box Score

Source: R/kp_box_tables.R
kp_box.Rd

Get KenPom Game Box Score

Usage

kp_box(game_id, year)

Arguments

game_id

Game id of game to pull

year

Year of game to pull

Value

Returns a tibble of game box scores

Examples

# \donttest{
  try(kp_box(game_id = 6, year = 2021))
